{"id": "sec-mode-dispatch-supplement-01", "prompt": "Mira, 我在更新 COHR 的 thesis，顺手从最新 10-Q 里帮我核实一下 share count 和 SBC 就行，不用拆全文。", "behavior": "sec_supplement_not_deep_dive", "rationale": "补事实核验且用户明说不拆全文 → sec_supplement 模式：补到当前研究包（sec-supplement-source-note + evidence log），不得膨胀成 sec_filing_deep_dive 全文解剖；只有口径冲突才升级。锁定同 skill 双模式分流。", "contract_refs": ["data/routing-index.csv sec_supplement", "loops/analysis-routing.md Step 1 sec_supplement", "skills/sec-filing-analysis/SKILL.md"], "routing_tokens": {"task_mode": "sec_supplement"}, "must_contain_all": [["share count", "股本", "股份数"], ["SBC", "股权激励", "stock-based compensation"], ["supplement", "补充", "核验"]], "must_not_contain": [], "severity": "error"}
{"id": "followup-none-waiver-01", "prompt": "Mira, 把这句原样存为我的 working view，不用展开分析，也别反问我：『COHR 在 CPO 放量中受益，但 2026 下半年才有订单证据』。", "behavior": "followup_none_explicit_waiver", "rationale": "用户明确不要反问 + 机械保存任务 → 不输出追问，但不得静默省略：必须显式 followup_prompt_mode=none + waiver 理由；保存走 view_continuity / private state。锁定豁免路径，防止反向仪式化（永远加追问）。", "contract_refs": ["OPERATING_CONTRACT.md follow-up waiver", "loops/analysis-routing.md Step 4.5 Final Gate", "loops/view-continuity-loop.md"], "routing_tokens": {"followup_prompt_mode": "none"}, "must_contain_all": [["followup_waiver_reason", "waiver", "豁免"], ["working_view", "working view"], ["private", "私有", "save_working_view"]], "must_not_contain": ["## Progressive Follow-Up", "下一步最有用的问题"], "severity": "error"}
